CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

September 14, 2006

[Cite as 09/14/2006 Case Announcements, 2006-Ohio-4732.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2004-0638. Nationwide Ins. Co. v. Phelps.

Columbiana App. No. 03 CO 23, 2004-Ohio-1200. This cause came on for further consideration of appellants’ motion to vacate the judgment of July 14, 2004. Upon consideration thereof,

It is ordered by the court that the motion is denied.
